title: National Autonomous Federation of Football of Honduras
text: The National Autonomous Federation of Football of Honduras (), known as FENAFUTH, is the official <a href="association%20football">football</a> governing body in <a href="Honduras">Honduras</a> and is in charge of the <a href="Honduras%20national%20football%20team">Honduras national team</a>. FENAFUTH was founded in 1935 and joined <a href="FIFA">FIFA</a> in 1946. It joined <a href="CONCACAF">CONCACAF</a> in 1961.
